  "description": "A picturesque coastal scene featuring a dark, sandy beach meeting the turquoise waters of the ocean. Dramatic, layered cliffs with vegetation rise up on the left side of the frame, displaying shades of brown, green, and reddish hues. The cliffs have visible caves and crevices carved by the sea. Gentle waves are rolling onto the shore, creating white foam as they break. The sky is a clear, bright blue. There appears to be a small figure of a person on the beach, providing scale to the expansive landscape. The overall impression is one of natural beauty and tranquility.",
